  <div class="wave" style="background:#f5f6fb"><svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M0,60 C480,0 960,0 1440,60 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#05091a"/></svg></div>

  <section class="mid-cta" aria-label="Newsletter CTA">
    <div class="mid-cta-inner">
      <div>
        <h2>Ready to Grow Your Business?</h2>
        <p>Book a free 30-minute strategy call. We'll review your marketing and show you exactly what's holding your business back.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary btn-large">Book My Free Call &rarr;</a>
